						<p>On a stone built into the trough receiving the sacred <hi rend="italic">tīrtha</hi> in the Doḍḍa Mallēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Āṅgīrasa, Āshāḍha ba. 30.</hi></p>						

						<p>It records the construction of the temple by Maṁtra[yya], son of Kṛishṇaya of Velaṁgapūṁḍi, a servant of god Doḍḍa Mallikārjuna.</p>						

